nodes.text: This sentient species existed in the galaxy.
The species had green or tan colored skin.
When Gannis Ducain, who stole the Millennium Falcon from Han Solo, was present in Canto Bight, a member of this species was also present there.
During 34 ABY, a member was present in Canto Bight while Finn and Rose Tico were searching for the Master Codebreaker.
